namicAnswers from saved JSON ─────────────────────────\r\n                                Clear(colDynamicAnswers);\r\n                                Clear(colDynamicMultiAnswers);\r\n                                If(\r\n                                    !IsBlank(ThisItem.'Dynamic Answers'),\r\n                                    ForAll(\r\n                                        ParseJSON(ThisItem.'Dynamic Answers'),\r\n                                        Collect(colDynamicAnswers, {\r\n                                            QuestionId:    GUID(Text(ThisRecord.QuestionIdText)),\r\n                                            QuestionLabel: Text(ThisRecord.QuestionLabel),\r\n                                            AnswerText:    Text(ThisRecord.AnswerText),\r\n                                            AnswerBool:    Boolean(ThisRecord.AnswerBool),\r\n                                            AnswerDate:    If(\r\n                                                               IsBlank(Text(ThisRecord.AnswerDate)),\r\n                                                               Blank(),\r\n                                                               DateTimeValue(Text(ThisRecord.AnswerDate))\r\n                                                           )\r\n                                        })\r\n                                    )\r\n                                );\r\n\r\n                                // ── 7. Set wizard position & navigate ───────────────────────────────────\r\n                                Set(varWizardMode,        \"Resume\");\r\n                                Set(varWizardStep,        1);\r\n                                Set(varGateStep,          0);\r\n                                Set(varIntakeFormVisible, false);\r\n                                Set(varTriggerScrollReset, true);\r\n                                Navigate(scrIntakeWizard, ScreenTransition.Fade)"
